---
title: Bacon and Mushroom Bourguignon with Fresh Fusilli Noodles
description: Our twist on the classic bourguignon doesn't have to simmer for hours on the stovetop. The secret? Using flavourful smoked bacon instead of stewing beef!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bacon-and-mushroom-bourguignon-2778b5ea.jpg
